      <Comment><![CDATA[RESET PHILOSOPHY: RESET CAN BE DONE EITHER FROM HARDWIRED BUTTON ON CONTROL PANEL OR THROUGH HMI SOFT PUSH BUTTON AFTER ALL CAUSES HAVE BECOME HEALTHY
]]></Comment>
